---
/* ProblemAgitation — Makes visitors feel the pain before presenting the solution */
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="fade-in-up space-y-4 mb-8">
      <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
        You <span class="text-text-primary font-semibold">think at 150 words per minute</span>.
        You type at 40.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-text-secondary text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Every day, ideas slow down between your brain and your keyboard.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="fade-in-up font-headline font-semibold text-accent-teal text-xl md:text-2xl" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
      What if your words just appeared — already polished?
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
